   megagametophyte},
Keywords-Plus = {DOUBLE FERTILIZATION; SEXUAL REPRODUCTION; FEMALE GAMETOPHYTE;
   EVOLUTION; GNETACEAE; EMBRYO},
Research-Areas = {Plant Sciences},
